title: Sandbox Live In Quebec -Bubbles of the Trailer Park Boys -repost
description:
Bubbles from the Trailer Park Boys old band Sandbox - Early 1997 - Live in Quebec Opening for Big Sugar

Here is a rare live show from Sandbox opening up for Big Sugar. This is Bubbles&#039; band before he got famous with the Trailer Park Boys. 

A friend gave me the tape at school and I am ripping all my stuff from casette -This might be the only live show out there by Sandbox..It&#039;s not bad quality -some songs are way better live - and there are some different lyrics and versions and even a song never heard before. Enjoy. 

1. Self Contained - different lyrics
2. Spin - 
3. Collide - 
4. Lustre - 
5. New Song - Unreleased
6. Here and There -
7. Too Red - different lyrics 
8. Curious - with story!
9. Melt -
